title: DigitalTutors Mastering CSS Animations Tutorial
description:
DigitalTutors Mastering CSS Animations Tutorial

In this CSS tutorial, you gain a solid understanding
of how CSS animations work, as well as practical experience
when implementing them. We'll dedicate the first few
lessons towards experimenting with the various CSS
properties that make animations work. Then we'll create a
PNG-based sprite animation, powered by CSS. And then
finally, we'll create a thumbnail gallery with responsive
CSS animations
